{"tid":818701,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"真無線藍芽耳機講電話得一邊聲係咪正常?","createTime":"2018-09-14T09:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T11:52:34.000Z","uid":10398,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1205849da1bb2ea8c734ba315e5156be07b81170","tid":818701,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:28:55.000Z","msg":"如題? <br />\n<br />\n上網搵過好似係正常? 定係個別耳機型號先會咁?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 岩岩買左zolo liberty+<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ5: 使用雙耳模式時，為何只有藍芽通話時只有一邊耳機有聲音?<br />\n<br />\nA5: 根據藍芽4.2安全性規範，當接收端與發送端同時發送訊號時，只能接受有一個實體的位置(一耳藍芽耳機)同時收與發，因此我們無法違反國際藍芽組織規定把通話模式設計成雙耳共用"},{"pid":"70f08820d96e0d86bb7714bbd6872bf6192f63ce","tid":818701,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"聽歌係兩邊都有聲"},{"pid":"21cde5711304912ca7f8ea8af3ce8f186b35f296","tid":818701,"uid":50676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"9ccb881be86161ca5eba0dd35e32ff64682d7b8b","tid":818701,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21cde5711304912ca7f8ea8af3ce8f186b35f296","tid":818701,"uid":50676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d77900bc732cee48eaf470fc25e05eb766a5317","tid":818701,"uid":152559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"AirPods 講電話係兩邊都有聲<br />\n但收音會自動揀是但一邊 mic 收音, 至於揀邊一邊收音個機制, 我冇去深究"},{"pid":"22f74922b6c8c383530ede09b2d617cce5ecbb19","tid":818701,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d77900bc732cee48eaf470fc25e05eb766a5317","tid":818701,"uid":152559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"AirPods 講電話係兩邊都有聲<br />\n但收音會自動揀是但一邊 mic 收音, 至於揀邊一邊收音個機制, 我冇去深究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:17:48.00